<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū dīng shí jià wèi jiù wàn mín, xìn kào tā de rén bì méng lián mǐn.
 zhǔ shì wǒ men dé jiù de zhōng bǎo, jīn shēng jīn shì tā bì zhǐ yǐn.
 shù yǒu gēn cái shēng bù xī, shuǐ yǒu yuán cái liú bù jǐn.
 zhǔ yǒu ài cái shí shí chuán sòng, yào jiāng fú yīn chuán biàn wàn guó wàn mín.</lyrics>
<title>yé sū dīng shí jià wèi jiù wàn mín 迦南1099</title>
